description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Symphony Healthcare Services Ltd (&quot;SHS&quot;) was established in 2016 as part of the award winning Symphony Programme Vanguard developing new models of care. With a growing network of 14 practices and 40 employed GPs in Somerset, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;The Meadows is a well-established dispensing practice in a purpose-built building which joined the SHS team in November 2018. Our integrated, multidisciplinary team which includes ECPs, a Counsellor and Medicines Management provides a wide range of services to around 4000 patients. The Meadows Surgery is also part of the CLICK federation of practicescovering Chard, Ilminster and Langport.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are now recruiting for2 regular GP sessions with occasional annual leave cover. The regular sessions would be every Thursday, on call duty GP 08:00 – 18:30, flexible working options, competitive remuneration package and Tier 2 Visa sponsorship available&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We offer our GPs a range of flexible working options together with a competitive remuneration package based on the BMA GP contract with additional incentive payments and further allowances for GPs with specialist skills and experience. Tier 2 Visa sponsorship available.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;For more information or to arrange an informal visit, please contactHayley Baker(Practice Manager) onhayley.baker6@nhs.net&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt; or 01460 52284&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
